1.0.1.readme:
# hubot-rational-brain

Hubot rational brain

See [`src/rational-brain.coffee`](src/rational-brain.coffee) for full documentation.

## Installation

In hubot project repo, run:

`npm install hubot-rational-brain --save`

Then add **hubot-rational-brain** to your `external-scripts.json`:

```json
[
  "hubot-rational-brain"
]
```

## Sample Interaction

```
user1>> hubot hello
hubot>> hello!
```

## NPM Module

https://www.npmjs.com/package/hubot-rational-brain
